WEBVTT

00:00:00.535 --> 00:00:02.773
-ST THE FIRST, NINETEEN NINETY FIVE.

00:00:03.336 --> 00:00:04.258
az

00:00:04.281 --> 00:00:08.733
MRS. RADOUSKI, mir zaynen yetst in fir un fertsikstn yor

00:00:08.733 --> 00:00:10.620
yo? in velkhe monat?

00:00:08.736 --> 00:00:09.995
ye, ye.

00:00:11.605 --> 00:00:13.272
zumer iz dos gevezn.

00:00:13.272 --> 00:00:14.479
mistome

00:00:14.479 --> 00:00:15.770
yun

00:00:15.770 --> 00:00:19.102
avgust, september, ⟨zaynen⟩ mir gevezn, ye.

00:00:18.000 --> 00:00:18.652
yo.

00:00:18.658 --> 00:00:20.174
un ir bahalt zikh

00:00:19.102 --> 00:00:20.306
biz vinter.

00:00:20.174 --> 00:00:23.124
un ir bahalt zikh yetst in a, in a vald

00:00:22.776 --> 00:00:27.022
in a vald zaynen mir gevezn. mir hobn mir avekgeshtelt PALATKES

00:00:27.467 --> 00:00:28.721
fun

00:00:28.721 --> 00:00:29.924
BREZENT

00:00:30.066 --> 00:00:31.562
un dortn hobn mir gelebt

00:00:33.137 --> 00:00:35.966
nu, un, mir hobn gearbet

00:00:36.006 --> 00:00:40.016
un me flegt undz hargenen, un esn hot men gegebn eyn mol

00:00:40.107 --> 00:00:41.198
in

00:00:41.608 --> 00:00:43.593
in tog, in ovnt

00:00:43.718 --> 00:00:44.929
a halbn liter

00:00:44.929 --> 00:00:46.648
vaser, mir flegn zukhn

00:00:47.177 --> 00:00:48.515
un in der fri

00:00:48.515 --> 00:00:51.519
ne- un, ye? in der fri, neyn, in ovnt

00:00:51.519 --> 00:00:55.659
a hundert gram broyt. dos flegn mir haltn shoyn oyf mo- in der fri.

00:00:56.813 --> 00:01:00.907
un mayn shvester flegt oyfesn glaykh dem zelbn t- ovnt

00:01:01.099 --> 00:01:05.025
un ikh fleg shrayen "loz iber oyf morgn," fleg zi zogn "ikh ken nit."

00:01:05.200 --> 00:01:09.261
UNK hot zi gevust az ikh es nit, un oyf morgn fleg ikh ir avekgebn.

00:01:10.026 --> 00:01:11.201
nu

00:01:11.899 --> 00:01:13.260
azoy

00:01:13.688 --> 00:01:17.192
a mol hot gebrakht a meydele, a shtume

00:01:17.367 --> 00:01:21.287
ikh veys nit fun vanet, fun UNK, mistome finf yor, hot zi gebrakht

00:01:21.287 --> 00:01:22.136
a k- a

00:01:22.463 --> 00:01:25.607
nit keyn arbuz, aza kirbes, kh'veys vos

00:01:25.607 --> 00:01:27.367
un zi hot gebrakht tsu shlepn

00:01:27.930 --> 00:01:29.881
un zi hot gekukt oyf mir

00:01:30.529 --> 00:01:34.201
az ikh zol nemen, un dem moment iz gek- ⟨tsufelik⟩ gegangen der daytsh

00:01:34.495 --> 00:01:41.728
un er hot gezogt "vu hostu geganvet?" hob ikh gezogt "ot di meydele." un di meydele hot nit farshtanen. zi hot nit gehert un nit geredt.

00:01:41.953 --> 00:01:45.592
hot er gezogt "du host geganvet, un du vest khapn klep.

00:01:45.717 --> 00:01:48.040
nor vos ikh gey itster oyfshnaydn"

00:01:48.602 --> 00:01:50.891
er shnaydt oyf in gantsn a farfoylte.

00:01:51.690 --> 00:01:53.422
hot er mir nit geharget.

00:01:55.588 --> 00:02:00.425
nu, un dan vos ikh dertseyl di, ven mir zaynen gegangen in WASHROOM

00:02:00.820 --> 00:02:02.704
ven mir zaynen gekumen tsurik

00:02:03.604 --> 00:02:06.433
⟨ze i-⟩ ruft er oyset dem NOMER

00:02:06.878 --> 00:02:08.576
un me nemt di ershte

00:02:08.734 --> 00:02:10.500
Mushele.

00:02:10.928 --> 00:02:12.592
un ikh her zi shrayt.

00:02:13.020 --> 00:02:14.687
un zi shrayt

00:02:14.687 --> 00:02:19.224
UNK tsvey m- tsvey soldatn hobn ir geharget, tsvey postns

00:02:19.467 --> 00:02:21.418
mit a shtekn UNK tsvey

00:02:21.492 --> 00:02:25.209
un zi hot, un zi hot kontik nit oysgehaltn, hot zi zikh gevorfn

00:02:25.209 --> 00:02:27.088
hot zi gekhapt iber di hent

00:02:27.398 --> 00:02:32.592
dernokh hot men geheysn ir brengen, hot men ir gebrakht a halb toyte, in gantsn a tseklapte

00:02:32.592 --> 00:02:34.972
UNK kop ⟨iberal, umetum⟩

00:02:34.972 --> 00:02:37.061
dernokh hot men aroysgerufn INGA.

00:02:37.573 --> 00:02:41.532
INGA hot gekhapt nor finf un tsvantsik shmits. zi hot nit geveynt.

00:02:41.573 --> 00:02:43.367
zi zi gevezn zeyer farbisn.

00:02:43.367 --> 00:02:45.246
hot zi gekhapt nor ibern

00:02:45.505 --> 00:02:49.197
o- iber, fun hintn. iber di hent hot zi nit gekrogn.

00:02:49.197 --> 00:02:51.894
m'hot ir gebrakht a toyte, un ikh hob zikh oyfgehoybn.

00:02:51.894 --> 00:02:53.744
m'hot mir gezogt az mir darf men nit.

00:02:54.617 --> 00:02:59.454
un ikh hob gevelt zeyer khapn klep, vayl mir iz zeyer nit gevezn ayngenem far di k- tsvey kinder.

00:03:00.304 --> 00:03:02.106
zey hobn gekhapt, un ikh nit.

00:03:02.106 --> 00:03:04.469
ikh hob dokh zey gezogt oyf do blaybn.

00:03:04.469 --> 00:03:06.570
bin gevezn az ikh hob zikh gefilt zeyer shlekht

00:03:06.570 --> 00:03:07.970
un ikh hob gevelt geyn

00:03:07.970 --> 00:03:13.190
hot er ibergezogt "az me ruft dir nit, iz gey nit." zog ikh "neyn, ikh vil khapn klep. ikh'l oyshaltn."

00:03:13.197 --> 00:03:15.536
ober er hot mir nit geharget.

00:03:17.500 --> 00:03:20.640
nu, un azoy flegn mir khapn, u- ikh fleg zen az UNK

00:03:20.640 --> 00:03:23.700
eyn mol hob ikh gezen az me geyt hargenen mayn shvester

00:03:24.368 --> 00:03:29.000
hob ikh zeyer gikh gelofn, un i- ven er hot oyfgehoybn dem shtekn, bin ikh tsugelof-

00:03:29.000 --> 00:03:31.280
kh'hob ir gegebn a shtup, un zi iz gefaln

00:03:31.280 --> 00:03:35.460
un er hot mir getrofn do. ven er git mir ibern kop volt ikh gevezn toyt.

00:03:35.460 --> 00:03:38.419
un ikh ho- bin gevezn gekhalesht shteyndikerheyt.

00:03:39.690 --> 00:03:41.695
er hot zikh antshuldikt far mir

00:03:41.695 --> 00:03:44.139
vayl er hot gevust az ikh arbet zeyer gut

00:03:44.331 --> 00:03:48.341
hot er zikh antshuldikt, nor ikh hob nit geentfert z- azoy dertseyln zey di froyen.

00:03:48.381 --> 00:03:52.273
hobn di froyen gezogt az zi hot farlorn dem bavustzayn. zi shteyt nor.

00:03:52.465 --> 00:03:56.762
zogt er "ya" zogt er. "ikh bet antshuldikn, ober der klap iz bay ir geblibn."

00:03:57.139 --> 00:04:02.246
⟨dan⟩ iz gevorn bay mir ot azoy gesh- biz danet, gegangen a torbe mit materye.

00:04:02.910 --> 00:04:04.839
hobn zey gevelt mit a britve

00:04:04.839 --> 00:04:06.667
aynshnaydn, hob ikh gezogt neyn.

00:04:06.842 --> 00:04:07.848
kh'loz nit.

00:04:08.361 --> 00:04:10.177
kh'hob gehat groyse veytogn.

00:04:10.707 --> 00:04:13.553
do iz gevezn bay mir di gantse fleysh

00:04:14.402 --> 00:04:17.433
aropgenumen do, vundn

00:04:18.334 --> 00:04:22.800
un kh'fleg geyn mit, mit di kleydl ot azoy vayl ikh hob nit gekent tsuleygn

00:04:23.211 --> 00:04:28.402
un ikh fleg darfn hakn mit di kirke di vortslen. vinter, dos iz gevezn shoyn vinter.

00:04:29.353 --> 00:04:30.792
nu, un dernokh

00:04:30.792 --> 00:04:33.177
hot men gezogt di rusn dernentern zikh.

00:04:33.454 --> 00:04:35.473
hot men undz geheysn aroysgeyn

00:04:35.867 --> 00:04:37.869
s- zaynen mir gevezn onderhalbn

00:04:38.128 --> 00:04:40.721
toyznt mistome froyen

00:04:41.368 --> 00:04:43.758
un ven mir hobn ongefangen marshirn

00:04:43.933 --> 00:04:45.041
vinter

00:04:45.655 --> 00:04:47.556
hot men genumen z- shlepn

00:04:48.574 --> 00:04:49.786
fun di reyen

00:04:49.786 --> 00:04:52.720
un ikh fleg alts gebn a kuk, ikh ze vi zey shisn.

00:04:52.810 --> 00:04:54.002
zey shisn.

00:04:54.058 --> 00:04:56.195
nor ven ikh hob nit gekent geyn

00:04:56.303 --> 00:04:58.387
bay mir iz gevezn do a vund ⟨un⟩

00:04:58.387 --> 00:05:02.077
do oykh gevezn a vund, azoy fil, ot di hant gehaltn azoy

00:05:02.209 --> 00:05:04.973
iz tsugeforn ot der daytsh mit a fur

00:05:04.973 --> 00:05:05.834
mit a vogn

00:05:05.834 --> 00:05:06.737
a ferd

00:05:06.737 --> 00:05:10.441
un gezogt "ver es ken nit geyn zoln zikh zetsn oyfn ferd."

00:05:10.441 --> 00:05:15.031
ikh bin gegangen, ober di Rivke ⟨zogt mir⟩ "du vest bay mir geyn un beser faln do

00:05:15.031 --> 00:05:16.027
nor gey nit."

00:05:16.027 --> 00:05:17.739
zog ikh "ikh ken nit geyn.

00:05:17.739 --> 00:05:19.975
kh'hob ⟨hoyle⟩ vundn, lekher."

00:05:19.975 --> 00:05:21.232
groyse vey geton.

00:05:21.232 --> 00:05:22.993
zogt zi "neyn, du vest geyn.

00:05:23.438 --> 00:05:26.776
UNK zey hot men arayngezetst, mistome a man

00:05:26.776 --> 00:05:27.869
fuftsn

00:05:28.146 --> 00:05:32.544
un zaynen gef- UNK geforn der ferd langzam, langzam, un mir hobn gedarft geyn.

00:05:33.040 --> 00:05:36.172
UNK mir gebn a kuk. der ferd kumt tsurik leydik.

00:05:36.617 --> 00:05:39.547
avekges- in vald, zey opgeshosn.

00:05:40.110 --> 00:05:42.956
a tsveytn mol hot er gefregt. ikh bin nit gegangen.

00:05:43.030 --> 00:05:44.340
⟨nit gegangen⟩

00:05:44.700 --> 00:05:49.768
un s'iz gevezn zeyer kalt, un d- der eyn daytsh, mir hobn im gegebn a nomen

00:05:49.768 --> 00:05:51.224
"zhurnalist".

00:05:51.366 --> 00:05:53.739
er iz gevezn a zhurnalist, a yunger.

00:05:54.083 --> 00:05:56.122
er flegt zeyer fil trinken.

00:05:56.122 --> 00:06:02.767
er iz geforn oyf a karetke, oyf a shlitn, mit a ferd, nor er flegt shteyn fun hintn oyf di

00:06:02.976 --> 00:06:05.436
ot di lines v- azoy

00:06:05.436 --> 00:06:06.820
un er flegt zen

00:06:06.820 --> 00:06:09.309
⟨az vi⟩ hingt, tsi me tsit a fus

00:06:09.309 --> 00:06:12.507
flegt er aropnemen, opshisn. mayn khaverte

00:06:12.507 --> 00:06:17.137
gegangen mit mir, hot zi gezogt "s'iz shlekht. kh'hob ongeribn di fus

00:06:17.137 --> 00:06:19.417
on di klu- on di hiltserne

00:06:19.446 --> 00:06:21.578
 shikh."

00:06:21.578 --> 00:06:22.911
zog ikh "halt zikh."

00:06:22.911 --> 00:06:25.616
un vi ikh hob gezogt "halt zikh" hot men ir aroysgenumen

00:06:25.909 --> 00:06:29.255
un ikh hob gezen vi er hot ir geshosn, hob ikh gezen vi zi iz gefaln

00:06:29.255 --> 00:06:33.815
un zikh oyfgehoybn. dos iz gevezn azoy interesant. ot dos vil ikh ⟨eybik⟩ geden-

00:06:33.815 --> 00:06:36.805
zi hot zikh avekgezetst, un dernokh iz zi gefaln.

00:06:37.182 --> 00:06:40.368
un azoy geyendik, un ikh hob alts gekukt fun hintn

00:06:40.368 --> 00:06:41.414
iz gevezn

00:06:41.414 --> 00:06:43.047
a opgezegte

00:06:43.797 --> 00:06:44.753
boym

00:06:44.944 --> 00:06:47.604
ot azoy gevezn, ye? un s'iz ful shney

00:06:47.762 --> 00:06:51.350
un ikh bin gegangen, kh'hob gekukt, un ikh hob zikh oysgeglitsht

00:06:51.897 --> 00:06:53.893
un ikh bin gefaln.

00:06:53.893 --> 00:06:55.755
un d- tseklapt do

00:06:56.976 --> 00:07:00.482
un, zey viln mir oyfheybn, zog ikh "ikh ken nit."

00:07:00.482 --> 00:07:04.124
mayn shvester zogt "heyb zikh oyf." zog ikh "ir geyt. antloyft."

00:07:04.249 --> 00:07:05.562
un ikh bin geblibn

00:07:05.562 --> 00:07:11.229
vayl ts- eyn shvester iz oykhet gefaln, di tsveyte iz geblibn. er iz tsugeforn. er hot zey ⟨beydn opgeshosn⟩.

00:07:11.438 --> 00:07:14.554
un ikh hob shoyn geshpirt az ikh muz zikh hoybn. ikh ken nit.

00:07:14.695 --> 00:07:17.307
ikh ⟨glitsh zikh oyset⟩ un ikh fal vayter di

00:07:17.307 --> 00:07:19.413
di shikh tsvey un fertsik

00:07:19.639 --> 00:07:24.729
der gantser knafl aropgehakt un der fornt azoy ⟨grob⟩. bin ikh gegangen, kh'hob zikh geglitsht.

00:07:25.866 --> 00:07:29.032
un mayn shvester mit, mit di Rive

00:07:29.055 --> 00:07:33.875
zey hobn geveynt, un zey n- un di vayber hobn zey avekgeshlept, un ikh bin geblibn.

00:07:34.101 --> 00:07:38.803
un ikh her shoyn, er fort shoyn mitn ferd UNK tik tak, tik tak, di gleklekh.

00:07:41.307 --> 00:07:42.803
kh'hob farmakht di oygn

00:07:43.028 --> 00:07:47.038
un er hot mir gerufn ma- dem nomen mir "BLUTWURST."

00:07:47.213 --> 00:07:51.898
bay poyerim makht men fun khazer fun di blut vursht. veyst ir vos

00:07:52.647 --> 00:07:54.970
iz bay mir a mol gevezn royt di bakn

00:07:55.077 --> 00:07:57.349
hot ir mir gegebn a nomen BLUTWURST

00:07:58.063 --> 00:08:00.001
un ikh ze er tantst aroys

00:08:00.001 --> 00:08:03.376
un er nemt aropet dem biks, un er geyt mir opshisn

00:08:03.376 --> 00:08:06.582
zogt er "BLUTWURST, vi iz b- vos tustu do?"

00:08:06.582 --> 00:08:08.149
zog ikh "ikh bin gefaln."

00:08:08.172 --> 00:08:09.617
zogt er "heyb zikh."

00:08:10.028 --> 00:08:10.759
zog ikh

00:08:10.759 --> 00:08:15.084
"ikh ken dokh nit heybn. ⟨ir zet?⟩ ikh heyb zikh un ikh fal vayter. ikh heyb zikh un ikh fal vayter."

00:08:15.192 --> 00:08:16.890
nemt er mir di hant

00:08:17.200 --> 00:08:19.573
un er heybt mir oyf un er zogt "loyf."

00:08:19.866 --> 00:08:24.618
vos hob ikh gemeynt? az ikh, loyfndik vet er mir shisn, bin ikh gelofn mit farmakhte oygn.

00:08:24.810 --> 00:08:27.910
un azoy farmakhte, ikh shpir, men khapt mir onet.

00:08:27.910 --> 00:08:30.200
ikh oyfn oyf, ikh ze di, mayn shvester

00:08:30.463 --> 00:08:31.523
di Rivke.

00:08:31.523 --> 00:08:33.005
ikh bin gor in kolone.

00:08:33.433 --> 00:08:36.312
ikh bin geblibn lebn. dos iz bin ikh eyne gevezn

00:08:36.589 --> 00:08:37.477
azoy.

00:08:38.344 --> 00:08:40.610
nu, un dernokh hot men undz arayngefirt

00:08:40.610 --> 00:08:41.694
bay nakht.

00:08:42.613 --> 00:08:44.922
mir zaynen gef- -gangen a gantse nakht.

00:08:44.922 --> 00:08:48.919
in mitn nakht zaynen mir UNK gekumen b- bay a poyer

00:08:49.937 --> 00:08:51.855
a UNK a daytshisher poyer

00:08:52.536 --> 00:08:59.696
un er hot, der daytshisher poyer hot gefregt efsher gebn zey esn. mir zaynen shoyn geblibn mistome vos far a

00:08:59.696 --> 00:09:03.029
dray hundert mentshn. alemen unt- opgeshosn.

00:09:03.029 --> 00:09:05.355
di gantse tsayt, m'hot geshosn, geshosn.

00:09:05.530 --> 00:09:07.836
z- zey hobn gevelt poter vern fun undz.

00:09:07.977 --> 00:09:13.219
vos veyniker mentshn. nem antloyft zey un di rusn yogn? antloyf? neyn, zey hobn gevelt shisn.

00:09:13.849 --> 00:09:15.559
hot, vos hot er geton?

00:09:15.559 --> 00:09:18.754
er hot oysgekokht hober vos me git far ferd

00:09:20.025 --> 00:09:23.430
un arayngeshotn i- avu di ferd esn, a-

00:09:23.451 --> 00:09:24.626
di lange

00:09:25.273 --> 00:09:26.865
vu zey esn, di ferd

00:09:26.865 --> 00:09:28.356
⟨s'hert zikh⟩ ferd

00:09:28.665 --> 00:09:31.868
un dortn hobn zey arayngegosn. mir hobn zikh geshtelt in rey

00:09:31.868 --> 00:09:32.999
un m'hot gegebn

00:09:32.999 --> 00:09:34.464
ikh hob gehat aza min

00:09:34.993 --> 00:09:39.340
a kvort, a, a sheper, aza min top, gehaltn di gantse tsayt

00:09:40.258 --> 00:09:43.964
un m'hot genumen gebn. ale hobn genumen esn.

00:09:44.106 --> 00:09:49.393
un ikh hob genumen. kh'hob ⟨dokh⟩ tsugeleygt tsum moyl, ikh, zog ikh "ikh shpir ferd."

00:09:49.393 --> 00:09:52.976
s'iz mir gevorn shlekht, hob ikh genumen, kh'hob oysgegosn oyf kerik

00:09:53.252 --> 00:09:55.321
i- dortn, zog ikh "ikh es nit."

00:09:55.395 --> 00:09:59.911
di Rivke hot oyf mir geshrien "far vos host dos geton? ikh volt oyfgegesn."

00:10:00.272 --> 00:10:03.298
nor far derayn vos ikh hob o- ayngegosn

00:10:03.298 --> 00:10:07.286
hot er gezogt "mer vest keyn mol nit krign keyn esn," un er hot mir genumen hargenen.

00:10:07.393 --> 00:10:08.698
kh'hob keyn mol nit geveynt.

00:10:08.698 --> 00:10:10.391
bin geven zeyer farbisn

00:10:11.511 --> 00:10:17.225
nu, un mir zaynen geblibn nekhtikn, un oyf morgn in der fri

00:10:17.552 --> 00:10:19.571
ver es ken zol aroysgeyn

00:10:20.708 --> 00:10:27.311
iz aroysgegangen a sakh froyen. a sakh zaynen geblibn fa- shoyn toyte. lebn mir iz gelegn eyne a froy

00:10:27.311 --> 00:10:31.671
hob ikh ir gevekt, kler ikh "vos bay ir iz di noz gevorn lang?" hob ikh ir gegebn a nem on

00:10:31.744 --> 00:10:33.375
zogn zey "zi iz toyt."

00:10:34.765 --> 00:10:38.404
nu, mir zaynen aroys, un mir hobn vayter marshirt, un vayter hot men geshosn.

00:10:38.511 --> 00:10:39.821
geshosn

00:10:40.367 --> 00:10:43.427
un dernokh zaynen mir arayn vayter in a tsveytn

00:10:43.427 --> 00:10:44.394
dorf

00:10:44.569 --> 00:10:46.301
hot men gegebn

00:10:46.662 --> 00:10:48.394
vos far di khazeyrim

00:10:48.822 --> 00:10:49.991
kartofl

00:10:49.991 --> 00:10:52.967
mit shtroy shtekhediker

00:10:53.479 --> 00:10:56.834
hot, nor take nit gegebn. di Rivke iz avek bay nakht

00:10:56.834 --> 00:10:57.726
un zi hot

00:10:57.934 --> 00:11:00.138
arayngeleygt in kleydl

00:11:00.364 --> 00:11:02.788
un zi iz gekumen in saray

00:11:02.828 --> 00:11:05.150
un zi hot gezogt "kh'hob geganvet esn."

