00:22:16.663 --> 00:22:18.862
m'hot undz gedarft alemen dershisn.

00:22:18.862 --> 00:22:19.746
griber.

00:22:20.443 --> 00:22:23.039
un Rivke heyst mir zikh oyfheybn

00:22:23.039 --> 00:22:24.541
un ikh ken shoyn nit.

00:22:24.541 --> 00:22:27.373
bin shoyn gevezn zeyer krank, un mayn shvester

00:22:28.206 --> 00:22:31.510
ober zi hot mir geheysn aroysgeyn. mir geyen aroys. mir gebn a kuk

00:22:31.510 --> 00:22:32.874
tankes forn.

00:22:34.281 --> 00:22:39.472
un eyner a dayt- eyner a rusisher yat iz tsugelofn tsu undz

00:22:40.018 --> 00:22:42.410
un mir hobn nit farshtanen vos er loyft.

00:22:42.410 --> 00:22:47.153
er hot derzen a daytsh iz aribergelofn di veg tsu undz

00:22:47.153 --> 00:22:48.967
zikh bahaltn hinter undz

00:22:48.967 --> 00:22:52.365
un der daytsh iz gevezn der glavner vos er hot undz gefirt

00:22:52.472 --> 00:22:54.001
un er hot geshosn

00:22:54.362 --> 00:22:57.785
un ven der, der rus iz tsugegangen, hot er gegebn a geshrey

00:22:57.785 --> 00:22:59.165
"ikh bin nit shuldik."

00:23:00.690 --> 00:23:01.607
nu

00:23:01.607 --> 00:23:04.414
un ven er hot gezogt "ikh bin nit shuldik"

00:23:04.605 --> 00:23:07.957
i- hot men im arayngehakt a mes- ye, im geshosn.

00:23:08.031 --> 00:23:09.606
er iz oykhet azoy gefaln

00:23:09.606 --> 00:23:16.415
un eyner a poylisher, a plenik, tsugelofn un im arayngehakt mit a meser un UNK gegebn a ⟨gants ibern⟩ gantsn boykh

00:23:16.415 --> 00:23:18.583
un ikh hob derzen, s'iz gevezn kalt.

00:23:18.583 --> 00:23:22.962
ikh hob derzen es bavekt zikh alts bay im. di kishkes alts, un a pare geyt

00:23:22.962 --> 00:23:24.810
bin ikh tsu, ikh hob gehaltn di hent

00:23:24.810 --> 00:23:26.081
s'iz gevezn kalt.

00:23:26.948 --> 00:23:28.545
nu, un

00:23:28.686 --> 00:23:31.644
un zi iz aroyfgegangen oyf a daytshishe fur

00:23:31.644 --> 00:23:37.168
di Rivke, un zi hot genumen far mir, tsu mir varfn produktn, un ikh hob alts genumen esn.

00:23:37.258 --> 00:23:38.838
un dos iz gevezn nit gut.

00:23:39.368 --> 00:23:46.123
genumen alts esn. s'iz tsugelofn a rus un gezogt "nit esn." hob ikh nit farshtanen. kh'hob gemeynt er vil tsunemen, hob ikh genumen shrayen

00:23:46.123 --> 00:23:49.115
hot er gemakht mir ot azoy az ikh bin a meshugene

00:23:49.881 --> 00:23:54.735
nu, un, m- m'hot undz arayngefirt in a daytshishe shtibl UNK

00:23:54.758 --> 00:24:00.506
un hot gevolt undz avekleygn in bet. hob ikh gezogt "ikh vil nit, vayle ikh bin nit ayngevoynt. UNK ikh vil lign oyf der erd."

00:24:00.613 --> 00:24:04.150
hot zi gebrakht h- shtroy. kh'hob zikh avekgeleygt oyf der erd

00:24:04.360 --> 00:24:06.159
un ikh hob ongefangen esn.

00:24:06.621 --> 00:24:08.133
ongefangen esn

00:24:08.173 --> 00:24:09.483
zeyer a sakh

00:24:09.507 --> 00:24:12.504
un ikh hob zikh oyf⟨UNK⟩, bin ikh shoyn gelegn in HOSPITAL.

00:24:13.017 --> 00:24:17.280
ober mayn shvester hot men nit genumen vayl zi iz shoyn gevezn vi hundert yor.

00:24:17.657 --> 00:24:22.277
vi ken a mentsh zen azoy, in hoyle sk- a skelet iz zi geven. hundert yor

00:24:22.277 --> 00:24:25.467
vayl me hot gezogt zi iz oykhet krank, ⟨hobn zey⟩ gezogt STARUKHA.

00:24:25.467 --> 00:24:27.574
aza alte, zi darf shtarbn.

00:24:28.187 --> 00:24:32.433
nu, un ikh bin gelegn. kh'hob gekrogn boykh tif mit a baysung.

00:24:33.452 --> 00:24:37.546
bin gelegn mistome dray vokhn. dernokh dem hot men undz aroysgefirt.

00:24:38.852 --> 00:24:42.474
mir hobn nit farshtanen ven s'iz nakht, ven s'iz fartog.

00:24:42.548 --> 00:24:47.708
e- d- me hot zikh geharget, nokh gekemft, un di rusn flegn arayngeyn zogn nit esn bay nakht

00:24:47.708 --> 00:24:49.275
zol zayn fintster

00:24:49.399 --> 00:24:53.426
un mir hobn nit gevust az dos iz bay nakht, me darf shlofn. mir hobn nit gevust.

00:24:53.922 --> 00:24:58.269
nu, biz vanet mir hobn zikh ayngeshtelt a bisl. dernokh hot men undz aroysgefirt

00:24:58.495 --> 00:25:00.176
dortn in shtetl

00:25:00.418 --> 00:25:02.150
⟨FRIEDHAUF⟩ dakht mir

00:25:02.190 --> 00:25:05.221
un, hot men gegebn a prikaz me zol aroysfirn

00:25:06.004 --> 00:25:08.059
oyf fabrikn in Rusland

00:25:08.029 --> 00:25:10.959
az, az ir zent arayn in ⟨FRIEDHAUF⟩

00:25:08.059 --> 00:25:09.271
fanandernemen.

00:25:10.881 --> 00:25:13.474
⟨FRIEDHAUF⟩, ye, ye, a shtetl

00:25:11.488 --> 00:25:12.494
FRIEDHAUF.

00:25:13.986 --> 00:25:18.941
nu, mir hobn fanandergenumen. s'iz gevezn di ukraintses

00:25:19.167 --> 00:25:22.738
un mir hobn oykhet gearbet. mir zaynen gevezn zeyer veynik froyen

00:25:22.795 --> 00:25:27.699
mistome froyen fuftsn. mir hobn gearbet, un ikh bin nokh gevezn krank

00:25:27.722 --> 00:25:31.452
un m'hot fanandergenumen, un s'iz nit gevezn shoyn keyn trep.

00:25:31.452 --> 00:25:32.882
s'iz gevezn a bret mit

00:25:32.882 --> 00:25:34.719
ongeklapt mit shteklekh.

00:25:34.945 --> 00:25:38.342
hob ikh gedarft aroyfkrikhn fanandernemen di shroyfn

00:25:38.342 --> 00:25:40.052
iz dortn gevezn gas

00:25:40.598 --> 00:25:42.080
vate

00:25:42.080 --> 00:25:43.343
gloz vate

00:25:43.382 --> 00:25:47.733
un s'iz oyf mir aropgefaln, un ikh bin aropgefaln, un ikh bin geblibn vayter

00:25:47.733 --> 00:25:49.986
hot ir nokh do di ⟨kontn⟩, di vayse

00:25:49.986 --> 00:25:52.640
nokh eyn glik, oyf di fis un oyf di hent

00:25:52.849 --> 00:25:55.512
vayter hob ikh gelegn t- a monat tsayt

00:25:55.512 --> 00:25:59.582
vayl ikh hob nit gekent shoyn nit oyfshteyn. di UNK hot mir oyfgegesn di fleysh

00:25:59.582 --> 00:26:02.352
UNK dos alts UNK fun di lager.

00:26:03.312 --> 00:26:06.968
un dernokh mir iz, az ikh bin shoyn gevorn gezunt demol-

00:26:07.125 --> 00:26:11.911
mir gibn a kuk az, oykhet di froyen hobn geton zeyer nit gut mit undz

00:26:12.019 --> 00:26:14.021
mir zaynen geblibn fir meydlekh.

00:26:14.415 --> 00:26:16.572
s'iz dortn gevezn a dokter a yid

00:26:16.572 --> 00:26:18.150
a rusisher dokter

00:26:18.150 --> 00:26:19.252
fun Rusland

00:26:19.967 --> 00:26:21.190
UNK a gene-

00:26:21.190 --> 00:26:23.086
ofitser, ikh veys vos

00:26:23.086 --> 00:26:26.256
ye, m'hot mir gefirt shoyn aropnemen di fingers

00:26:26.616 --> 00:26:30.069
bin, hob ikh gehert vi me sh- di k- di meydlekh shrayen

00:26:30.413 --> 00:26:33.765
⟨BOLIT, BOLIT⟩. ikh hob nit farshtanen vos zey shrayen ⟨BOLIT⟩.

00:26:33.990 --> 00:26:37.440
dernokh, vos iz, ikh hob gehert TSH TSH

00:26:37.440 --> 00:26:40.008
zey hobn gezegt di fis.

00:26:40.875 --> 00:26:44.666
m'hot gezegt di fis. z- zey hobn gehat azelkhe veytog az zey hobn geshrien

00:26:44.790 --> 00:26:52.715
dernokh hot men mir avekgeleygt oyfn, oyfn tish, un m'iz gegangen shoyn mir aropnemen di fingers, iz gekumen a kleynem mayor, a yid

00:26:52.823 --> 00:26:55.956
a dokter, un er ⟨iz tsugegangen⟩ un er hot azoy gemakht

00:26:56.434 --> 00:27:00.697
un er git a kuk, es falt mir arop di fleysh, ober der beyn iz royt

00:27:01.429 --> 00:27:04.848
zogt er, zet, ir darf men nit shnaydn ⟨vayle⟩ der beyn

00:27:05.057 --> 00:27:10.108
nu, un ikh bin tsugegangen tsu mayne bakante, zaynen gelegn, ober vos, verem

00:27:10.108 --> 00:27:11.244
un zey zaynen a-

00:27:12.482 --> 00:27:13.387
avek

00:27:14.457 --> 00:27:15.345
reydn

00:27:15.705 --> 00:27:18.635
un avekgegangen oyfn front

00:27:18.675 --> 00:27:24.339
un di meydlekh hobn ⟨veytog geshrien⟩. ikh bin tsu, iz oyf di bandazh iz ge- UNK gegangen vayse veremlekh

00:27:24.430 --> 00:27:27.562
dos heyst, s'iz nokh nit gut gevezn aropgenumen.

00:27:27.602 --> 00:27:30.211
biz vanet zey zaynen gekumen zaynen zey geshtorbn

00:27:30.927 --> 00:27:32.845
un der yidisher dokter

00:27:33.458 --> 00:27:35.142
vos er hot e- ar-

00:27:35.142 --> 00:27:37.434
gekukt vi mir arbetn

00:27:37.525 --> 00:27:40.489
hot er gen- gezogt tsu, tsu eyne a froy

00:27:40.933 --> 00:27:44.271
az me ve- vet aykh alemen aroysfirn in Rusland

00:27:44.271 --> 00:27:46.023
mir hobn dernokh zikh dervust

00:27:46.519 --> 00:27:49.097
"oyb ir vilt, vel ikh aykh avekfirn"

00:27:49.097 --> 00:27:51.451
oyf di zone fun di amerikaner.

00:27:51.451 --> 00:27:53.482
hobn zey nit gezogt undz

00:27:54.838 --> 00:28:00.603
un mir kumen tsu geyn in, in lager dortn, UNK mir gibn a kuk, mir zaynen in gantsn finf meydlekh.

00:28:00.913 --> 00:28:02.594
vu zaynen di iberike?

00:28:02.668 --> 00:28:07.187
hobn mir zikh dernokh dervust az der dokter hot arayngeleygt in a mashin

00:28:07.187 --> 00:28:09.547
un zey tsugefirt bay di amerikaner.

00:28:10.026 --> 00:28:13.682
un undz hot men mit di ukraintses aroysgefirt in Rusland

00:28:15.156 --> 00:28:19.284
bay nakht mit hint, oykhet mit hint, di zelbe zakhn vi di daytshn.

00:28:20.185 --> 00:28:23.064
az dos iz shoyn in d- in may, y-

00:28:21.737 --> 00:28:25.511
in fin- dos iz gevezn in finf un fertsikstn yor

00:28:25.635 --> 00:28:26.844
in may

00:28:25.737 --> 00:28:27.303
i- neyn

00:28:27.188 --> 00:28:27.843
april

00:28:27.303 --> 00:28:31.648
⟨zikh, zikh⟩ bafrayt ⟨hot men⟩ mir in finf un fertsikstn in mart

00:28:31.648 --> 00:28:33.037
dem tsentn

00:28:33.988 --> 00:28:37.795
un dos iz gevezn mistome in avgust

00:28:38.562 --> 00:28:42.150
un mir hobn nit farshtanen vu me firt undz in vagones

00:28:42.831 --> 00:28:45.356
un ven mir zaynen gekumen in LVOV

00:28:46.881 --> 00:28:49.119
hot men oyf undz gevorfn shteyner

00:28:49.176 --> 00:28:50.452
di rusishe

00:28:51.522 --> 00:28:55.906
ongefangen varfn shteyner, un ikh bin arop, un ikh hob, bin gegangen

00:28:55.906 --> 00:29:00.948
dos ganvenen. kh'hob nit keyn gelt nit gehat, oyfn mark, mit a mol ze ikh di vagones forn.

00:29:01.917 --> 00:29:04.054
bin ikh nokhgelofn

00:29:04.600 --> 00:29:09.758
un ikh hob zikh aroyfgekhapt, un ikh hob gezogt tsi iz ongeshribn oyf di vagones vos

00:29:10.573 --> 00:29:12.642
derfar varft men di shteyner

00:29:12.818 --> 00:29:16.862
iz eyne a froy vos, kontik zi hot gekent leyenen oder vos

00:29:17.020 --> 00:29:19.818
iz gevezn ongeshribn az frayvilik zaynen zey

00:29:19.818 --> 00:29:23.494
geforn in, in daytshland, di ukraintses. dos iz rikhtik.

00:29:23.770 --> 00:29:25.654
ober mir zaynen arayngefaln.

00:29:25.677 --> 00:29:27.589
mir hobn gezogt mir zaynen yidn

00:29:27.589 --> 00:29:30.010
ober mir hobn nit gehat keyn papirn

00:29:30.010 --> 00:29:32.870
hot men gezogt in, in a, in Rusland

